'''Harker''' is a recurring background character in the [[Season 2|second season]]. He is played by an unidentified extra and debuts in &quot;[[The Ghost of Harrenhal]].&quot; Harker is a member of the [[Night's Watch]], a [[Ranger]] serving under [[Qhorin]]. He is killed by [[Free Folk|wildlings]] while scouting the [[Skirling Pass]].
